<style>
  /* ===== Bespoke: Process Section (Dark Luxury) ===== */
  .bmx-process {
    --ink: #f5f5f5;
    --muted: #a0a0a0;
    --paper: #252525;
    --accent: #D4AF37;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 100px 0 0 0;
  }

  .bmx-process::before {
    content: "♪ ♫ ♩ ♬";
    position: absolute;
    top: -40%;
    left: -10%;
    font-size: 300px;
    font-family: serif;
    color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05); /* Gold tint */
    transform: rotate(-15deg);
    letter-spacing: 40px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .bmx-process::after {
    content: "♩ ♫ ♬ ♪";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -35%;
    right: -5%;
    font-size: 280px;
    font-family: serif;
    color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05); /* Gold tint */
    transform: rotate(12deg);
    letter-spacing: 35px;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .bmx-process .wrap {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .bmx-process h2 {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
    font-size: 34px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .bmx-process p.sub {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto 56px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .bmx-process .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
    text-align: left;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    background: #2a2a2a;
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* Subtle spotlight on middle card */
  .bmx-process .step:nth-child(2) {
    background: #2a2a2a;
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
  }

  .bmx-process .num {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .bmx-process .title {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .bmx-process .text {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  @media(max-width: 900px){
    .bmx-process .steps{grid-template-columns: 1fr}
    .bmx-process .step{text-align: center}
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .bmx-process h2 { font-size: 28px; }
    .bmx-process p.sub { font-size: 16px; }
    .bmx-process .title { font-size: 18px; }
    .bmx-process .text { font-size: 15px; }
  }
</style>

<section class="bmx-process color-scheme-dark-luxury" aria-labelledby="bm-proc-title">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 id="bm-proc-title">How Your Song Comes to Life</h2>
    <p class="sub">
      Every song starts with a real story — yours. My goal is to understand what you feel and turn it into music that feels honest, beautiful, and lasting.
    </p>

    <div class="steps" role="list">
      <article class="step" role="listitem">
        <div class="num">1</div>
        <div class="title">The Consultation</div>
        <div class="text">
          We begin with a short written consultation where you share who the song is for, the moments that matter, and the feeling you want captured.
          You don’t need perfect words — just what’s true. I’ll shape it with care.
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="step" role="listitem">
        <div class="num">2</div>
        <div class="title">Writing & Collaboration</div>
        <div class="text">
          I craft lyrics and melody that bring your story to life, aiming to capture its heart — not just its details.
          You’ll review and approve the lyrics before I move into production, so every line feels right to you.
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="step" role="listitem">
        <div class="num">3</div>
        <div class="title">Production & Final Approval</div>
        <div class="text">
          Once the words are set, I produce the song using studio-quality AI tools and refine every note.
          You’ll have final approval before delivery — your song, exactly as it should be.
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  (function(){
    var steps = document.querySelectorAll('.bmx-process .step');
    if(!steps.length) return;
    if(!('IntersectionObserver' in window)){
      steps.forEach(s=>s.classList.add('visible'));
      return;
    }
    var obs = new IntersectionObserver(entries=>{
      entries.forEach(e=>{
        if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('visible');obs.unobserve(e.target);}
      });
    },{threshold:0.2});
    steps.forEach(s=>obs.observe(s));
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Process Section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Process Section"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
